### Get all discounts for shop
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: {{$dotenv AUTH_TOKEN}}
x-client-id: {{$dotenv X_CLIENT_ID}}
x-api-key: {{$dotenv X_API_KEY}}

### Delete discount
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{$dotenv AUTH_TOKEN}}
x-client-id: {{$dotenv X_CLIENT_ID}}
x-api-key: {{$dotenv X_API_KEY}}

{
  "code": "SHOP-1133"
}

### Get products with code
GET {{baseUrl}}/list-products?shopId=69c3b6ce0c5ac39c2105ebe0&code=SHOP-1155&limit=10&page=1
x-api-key: {{$dotenv X_API_KEY}}

### Get amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/amount
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{$dotenv X_API_KEY}}

{
  "shopId": "69c3b9aba22c7939928c963f",
  "userId": 2,
  "code": "SHOP-1133",
  "products": [
    {
      "productId": "69d0095fc2305ae916641efc",
      "quantity": 5,
      "price": 120000
    }
  ]
}